quran[74]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,Pamene ola la chiweruzo lidza
  56,2,Ndipo palibe mzimu umene udzakana kudza kwake
  56,3,Kutsitsa gulu lina ndikukweza gulu linzake
  56,4,Pamene dziko lidzagwedezeka ndi chigwedezo choopsya
  56,5,Ndi pamene mapiri adzafumbutuka kukhala fumbi lokhalokha
  56,6,Motero iwo adzakhala fumbi louluzika paliponse
  56,7,Ndipo inu mudzagawidwa m’magulu atatu
  56,8,Iwo a ku dzanja la manja. Kodi a ku dzanja la manja adzakhala ndani
  56,9,Iwo akudzanja la mazere. Kodi akudzanja la mazere adzakhala ndani
  56,10,Ndipo gulu la iwo amene adzakhala kutsogolo m’chikhulupiriro adzakhala kutsogolo m’moyo umene uli nkudza
  56,11,Awa ndiwo amene adzakhala kufupi ndi Mulungu
  56,12,M’minda ya Paradiso
  56,13,Gulu lalikulu lidzachokera ku mibadwo ya kale
  56,14,Ndi gulu lochepa lidzachokera ku mibadwo ya m’mbuyo mwake
  56,15,Iwo adzakhala pa mipando yawofowofo yomatidwa golide ndi miyala ya mtengo wapatali
  56,16,Atakhala pa iyo ndi kumayang’anizana
  56,17,Iwo adzatumikiridwa ndi anyamata a muyaya
  56,18,"Ndi mabakuli, miphika ndi zikho za vinyo wabwino"
  56,19,Amene sadzawawitsa mitu yawo kapena kuwatopetsa
  56,20,Ndi zipatso zimene adzasankhepo
  56,21,Ndi nyama ya nkhuku imene angafune
  56,22,"Ndipo padzakhala anzawo okongola, a maso akulu ndi ochititsa kaso"
  56,23,Monga ndolo zosamalidwa bwino
  56,24,Malipiro a ntchito zimene adachita kale
  56,25,Palibe nkhani zopanda pake kapena zolaula zimene adzamva
  56,26,"Kupatula mawu akuti Mtendere, Mtendere"
  56,27,"Iwo a kudzanja lamanja, kodi akudzanja lamanja adzakhala ndani"
  56,28,Iwo adzakhala pakati pa m’mithunzi ya mitengo ya Sidrah
  56,29,Ndi m’mapata a nthochi zokhala ndi mikoko wina pamwamba pa unzake
  56,30,M’mithunzi yotambasuka
  56,31,Pambali pa madzi osefukira
  56,32,Ndi zipatso zochuluka
  56,33,Zimene nyengo yake sikutha ndipo kuchuluka kwake kudzakhalabe
  56,34,Ndi pa mipando yawofowofo yokwezedwa
  56,35,Ndithudi Ife tawalenga iwo mu chilengedwe cha padera
  56,36,Ndi kuwapanga kukhala a Namwali abwino
  56,37,A chikondi pa anzawo olingana nawo zaka
  56,38,A iwo amene adzakhala kudzanja lamanja
  56,39,"Gulu lochuluka lidzakhala lochokera ku mibadwo yoyamba, yakale"
  56,40,Gulu lochuluka lidzakhala lochokera ku mibadwo ya pambuyo pake
  56,41,Gulu la anthu a kudzanja lamanzere. Kodi anthu a kudzanja la manzere adzakhala otani
  56,42,M’katikati mwa malawi a moto ndi m’madzi ogaduka
  56,43,Ndi m’mithunzi ya utsi wakuda
  56,44,Yosazizira kapena yabwino
  56,45,Ndithudi iwo kale adali kukhala m’moyo wosavutika ndi opeza zinthu zambiri
  56,46,Ndipo adapitirira kuchita zoipa zikulu zikulu
  56,47,"Ndipo iwo anali kukonda kunena kuti: “Pamene ife tafa ndi kusanduka fumbi ndi mafupa, kodi tingadzaukitsidwenso?”"
  56,48,“Ndi makolo athu a nthawi ya makedzana?”
  56,49,"Nena: “Ndithudi onse oyambirira ndi otsiriza.”"
  56,50,“Ndithudi onse adzasonkhanitsidwa pamodzi pa tsiku lokhazikitsidwa.”
  56,51,“Kuphatikiza inu nonse amene muchimwa ndi kukana choonadi.”
  56,52,“Ndithudi inu mudzadya zipatso za mtengo wa Zaqqoom.”
  56,53,“Ndipo mudzakhutitsa mimba zanu ndi izo.”
  56,54,“Ndi kumwa madzi ogaduka.”
  56,55,“Ndi kumwa monga momwe ngamira yodwala ndi yaludzu imamwera.”
  56,56,Kumeneko ndiko kudzakhala kusangalala kwawo patsiku lachiweruzo
  56,57,Ndife amene tidakulengani inu nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani simukhulupilira
  56,58,Ndiuzeni za umuna umene mumatulutsa
  56,59,Kodi ndinu amene mumaulenga kapena Ife ndife timaulenga
  56,60,Ife tidalamulira imfa kukhala pakati panu ndipo Ife sitingagonjetsedwe ayi
  56,61,Kukusinthani inu ndi kukulengani kukhala china chake chimene inu simuchidziwa
  56,62,Ndithudi inu mumadziwa za chilengedwe choyamba. Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani simulabadira
  56,63,Kodi mudayamba mwaganiza za mbewu imene mumabzala
  56,64,Kodi ndinu amene mumaimeretsa kapena ndife amene timameretsa
  56,65,"Ngati titafuna, Ife tikadaiphwanya m’timagawomagawo touma ndipo inu mukadayamba kudandaula"
  56,66,Ndithudi ife tapatsidwa chingongole cholemera
  56,67,Iyayi. Koma tamanidwa
  56,68,Kodi inu mumawaona madzi amene mumamwa
  56,69,Kodi ndinu amene mumawagwetsa kuchokera ku mitambo kapena ndife
  56,70,Chikadakhala chifuniro chathu tikadawapanga iwo kukhala a mchere. Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani simuthokoza
  56,71,Kodi inu mumaganizira za moto umene mumasonkha
  56,72,Kodi ndinu amene mumameretsa mtengo umene umayaka moto kapena ndife amene timaumeretsa
  56,73,Ife taupanga iwo kukhala chikumbutso ndi chinthu chothandiza anthu amene ali paulendo
  56,74,Kotero lemekezani dzina la Ambuye wanu Wamkulu